        <div class="col-md-9">
            <div class="shopyheader">
                <h2>{l s='Catalog management' mod='shopylinkerp'}</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-10 shopyinfopanel">
                <h2>{l s='Catalog management' mod='shopylinkerp'}</h2>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question1" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="question1">
                        {l s='How does Shopylinker improve catalog management in PrestaShop stores?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse in" id="question1">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="To make catalog management easier, Shopylinker offers an evolutionary workspace that is revolutionizing online store management. This visual and intuitive workspace consists of 5 specialized workspaces combined with the bulk actions container. The result is an informed, simple and quick management to carry out." mod='shopylinkerp'}

                            </p>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/catalog-management/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the Visual Catalog Management page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
