                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question3" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="question3">
                        {l s='What are Shopylinker work environments and what are they used for?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse " id="question3">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="To facilitate catalog management, Shopylinker provides 5 work environments, each of them specially designed to facilitate and speed up the performance of specific actions." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <p>
                                {l s="The 5 work environments provided by Shopylinker are: " mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <table class="infotable">
                                <tr>
                                    <th>{l s="Work environment" mod='shopylinkerp'}</th>
                                    <th>{l s="Actions" mod='shopylinkerp'}</th>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>{l s="Categories - Products" mod='shopylinkerp'}</td>
                                    <td>
                                        <p>{l s="Environment designed for:" mod='shopylinkerp'}</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>{l s="Assigning products to main or display categories" mod='shopylinkerp'}</li>
                                            <li>{l s="Individual and mass editions of products" mod='shopylinkerp'}</li>
                                            <li>{l s="Sort the products in the category listings shown on the front" mod='shopylinkerp'}</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>{l s="Categories - Subcategories" mod='shopylinkerp'}</td>
                                    <td>
                                        <p>{l s="Environment designed for:" mod='shopylinkerp'}</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>{l s="Create and modify the category structure" mod='shopylinkerp'}</li>
                                            <li>{l s="Edit the categories" mod='shopylinkerp'}</li>
                                        </ul>

                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>{l s="Facets - Products " mod='shopylinkerp'}</td>
                                    <td>
                                        <p>{l s="Environment designed for:" mod='shopylinkerp'}</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>{l s="Assign or unassign facets to products (features, tags, brands and attributes) individually or in bulk" mod='shopylinkerp'}</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>{l s="Brands - Products" mod='shopylinkerp'}</td>
                                    <td>
                                        <p>{l s="Environment designed for:" mod='shopylinkerp'}</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>{l s="Assign brands to products" mod='shopylinkerp'}</li>
                                            <li>{l s="Sort the products in the brand listings shown on the front" mod='shopylinkerp'}</li>
                                        </ul>

                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>{l s="Suppliers - Products" mod='shopylinkerp'}</td>
                                    <td>
                                        <p>{l s="Environment designed for:" mod='shopylinkerp'}</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>{l s="Assign vendors to products individually or in bulk" mod='shopylinkerp'}</li>
                                        </ul>

                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/catalog-management/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question4" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="question4">
                        {l s='Does Shopylinker have different display options to manage the catalog?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question4">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="Shopylinker gives you two display options." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s="In Tile mode, objects are presented as cards showing the most relevant properties of the object and have interactive buttons for quick access to editing specific properties. If you prefer to work in a more traditional way, you also have the option of using the List mode, which is similar to how it is displayed in the PrestaShop backoffice but adding the same accessibility options that Shopylinker's Mosaic mode offers." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a data-image-url="Modo_mosaico.png" data-target="#modalimg" class="linkinfo imagelink" href="#">{l s='Mosaic mode display' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Ver_imagen"></i></a><br>

                            <a data-image-url="Modo_listado.png" data-target="#modalimg" class="linkinfo imagelink" href="#">{l s='List mode display' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Ver_imagen"></i></a><br>

                            <a data-image-url="Ficha_producto_modo_mosaico.png" data-target="#modalimg" class="linkinfo imagelink" href="#">{l s='Mosaic mode product card' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Ver_imagen"></i></a><br>

                            <a data-image-url="Ficha_producto_modo_mosaico+info.png" data-target="#modalimg" class="linkinfo imagelink" href="#">{l s='Product card with additional information activated on hover' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Ver_imagen"></i></a><br>

                            <a data-image-url="Fila de producto en visualización modo Listado.png" data-target="#modalimg" class="linkinfo imagelink" href="#">{l s='Product row in List mode display' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Ver_imagen"></i></a><br>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question5" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="question5">
                        {l s='What are the differences between admin mode and store mode?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question5">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="In the environments 'Categories - Products', 'Categories - Subcategories' and 'Brands - Products' it is possible to select between the administrator mode and the store mode." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s="The administrator mode is the usual display mode to manage the catalog, the store mode allows you to work with the lists as they are displayed on the front of the store, in the store mode the elements of the list appear with the same pagination as on the front, and you can also activate the ordering of the elements of the list." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s="This display mode avoids having to carry out checks at the front of the store." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question6" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="question6">
                        {l s='What are quick action buttons and how are they used?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question6">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="Quick action buttons are located on the object cards in Tile view mode or in cells within the rows corresponding to the object in List mode. These buttons reflect the state of specific object properties, and you can access editing of the indicated property by simply clicking the corresponding button." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <a data-image-url="Ficha_producto_modo_mosaico+detalles_acc_rapidas.png" data-target="#modalimg" class="linkinfo imagelink" href="#">{l s='Quick action buttons Mosaic mode' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Ver_imagen"></i></a><br>

                            <a data-image-url="Ficha_producto_listado_detalles.png" data-target="#modalimg" class="linkinfo imagelink" href="#">{l s='List Mode Quick Action Buttons' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Ver_imagen"></i></a><br>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question7" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="question7">
                        {l s='What is the multi-action container?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question7">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="The multi-action container is a space where you can group products, categories, and other entities to perform bulk actions on selected items." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s="Each work environment has a MAC designed to act on the type of entities it groups." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s="The groups made can be saved as lists that can be retrieved later to carry out massive actions on the same elements." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <a data-image-url="Selección de productos MAC.png" data-target="#modalimg" class="linkinfo imagelink" href="#">{l s='Selection of MAC products' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Ver_imagen"></i></a><br>

                            <a data-image-url="Opciones del menú MAC.png" data-target="#modalimg" class="linkinfo imagelink" href="#">{l s='MAC Menu Options' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Ver_imagen"></i></a><br>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3265EDwyQ6s"
                               target="_blank">{l s='MAC Menu Options' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
